y 2019}}\n|MF\n|{{flagicon|NED}} [[Jackie Groenen]]\n|{{flagicon|GER}} [[1. FFC Frankfurt]]\n|<ref>{{cite news |title=Groenen agrees to sign for Manchester United Women |url=https://www.manutd.com/en/news/detail/Jackie-Groenen-agrees-to-sign-for-Manchester-United-Women |website=ManUtd.com |publisher=Manchester United |date=22 May 2019 |accessdate=8 September 2019 }}</ref>\n|-\n|1 July 2019{{efn|Deal agreed 24 May 2019}}\n|DF\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Abbie McManus]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Manchester City W.F.C.|Manchester City]]\n|<ref>{{cite news |title=McManus agrees to sign for United Women |url=https://www.manutd.com/en/news/detail/abbie-mcmanus-agrees-to-sign-for-manchester-united-women |website=ManUtd.com |publisher=Manchester United |date=24 May 2019 |accessdate=8 September 2019 }}</ref>\n|-\n|1 July 2019{{efn|Deal agreed 5 June 2019}}\n|MF\n|{{flagicon|WAL}} [[Hayley Ladd]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Birmingham City W.F.C.|Birmingham City]]\n|<ref>{{cite news |title=United Women reach agreement with Ladd |url=https://www.manutd.com/en/news/detail/united-women-agree-to-sign-welsh-midfielder-hayley-ladd |website=ManUtd.com |publisher=Manchester United |date=5 June 2019 |accessdate=8 September 2019 }}</ref>\n|-\n|4 July 2019\n|FW\n|{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Jane Ross (footballer)|Jane Ross]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[West Ham United F.C. Women|West Ham United]]\n|<ref>{{cite news |title=United Women sign Scotland striker Ross |url=https://www.manutd.com/en/news/detail/Scotland-striker-Jane-Ross-signs-for-Manchester-United-Women |website=ManUtd.com |publisher=Manchester United |date=4 July 2019 |accessdate=8 September 2019 }}</ref>\n|-\n|12 July 2019\n|GK\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Mary Earps]]\n|{{flagicon|GER}} [[VfL Wolfsburg (women)|VfL Wolfsburg]]\n|<ref>{{cite news |title=Manchester United Women sign Mary Earps |url=https://www.manutd.com/en/news/detail/Man-United-Women-agree-signing-of-Mary-Earps |website=ManUtd.com |publisher=Manchester United |date=12 July 2019 |accessdate=8 Septembe